---
---
<section
  data-test="problem-section"
  style="padding:4rem 1.5rem;background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"
>
  <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">The problem</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.75rem);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">
      AI agents drift.<br/>Specs prevent it.
    </h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.65;max-width:620px;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      Without a structured specification, AI coding agents make decisions based
      on incomplete context — leading to spec drift, inconsistency, and features
      that don't reflect your actual vision.
    </p>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;">
      <div style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;">
        <div style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🌀</div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Spec drift</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9375rem;line-height:1.6;">
          Each agent prompt diverges slightly from the last until the codebase no longer matches your intent.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;">
        <div style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🤖</div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">AI limitations</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9375rem;line-height:1.6;">
          LLMs lack persistent memory across sessions and cannot infer your product philosophy without explicit grounding.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;">
        <div style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">📜</div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Missing context</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9375rem;line-height:1.6;">
          Traditional PRDs and tickets were designed for humans, not AI agents that need structured, queryable context.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
